248
00:29:16,007 --> 00:29:18,379
Oh, my God! Did you see that?

249
00:29:18,926 --> 00:29:20,634
Jeez, it's so bloody.

250
00:29:20,678 --> 00:29:23,513
Yeah, they're lucky,
that matador was very good.

251
00:29:23,596 --> 00:29:26,170
- It's much worse when they're mediocre.
- Why?

252
00:29:26,224 --> 00:29:29,807
