and I don't want you to lose your shit.

278
00:31:00,468 --> 00:31:02,210
Lose my shit?

279
00:31:03,261 --> 00:31:05,549
My God, what are you gonna tell me?

280
00:31:05,679 --> 00:31:07,506
Sometimes...

281
