Cooperate gigs?

300
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:32,165
- Think what you will.
- It's ridiculous!

301
00:32:32,209 --> 00:32:33,868
- Yes.
- Cooperate gigs.

302
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:36,331
Yes...! My God...

