326
00:34:09,871 --> 00:34:12,742
- The "gotta pee"-theory.
- You're catching on.

327
00:34:12,791 --> 00:34:15,459
- Now... escape-routes.
- Escape-routes?

328
00:34:15,501 --> 00:34:17,124
- You don't wanna get caught, right?
- No, no...

329
00:34:17,168 --> 00:34:18,580
- Don't get caught, it sucks.
