- You said money was no object.

376
00:38:03,185 --> 00:38:05,012
Bingo! Was his name...!

377
00:38:05,062 --> 00:38:06,604
- This is what you wanted, right?
- No!

378
00:38:06,647 --> 00:38:08,686
- This is what you helped with.
- I didn't help you!

379
00:38:08,732 --> 00:38:11,223
- Oh, yes you did...
- No, no, no!

380
00:38:14,362 --> 00:38:16,188
Oh God, no...!

381
00:38:26,455 --> 00:38:28,281
Fun, eh?

382
00:38:30,291 --> 00:38:32,117
Come on!

383
00:38:34,586 --> 00:38:36,911
That was incredible,
you scared the hell out of me!

384
00:38:36,963 --> 00:38:40,046
- You liked that, didn't you?
- I really bought it.

385
00:38:40,507 --> 00:38:44,968
A stranger...
just like that!

386
00:38:45,178 --> 00:38:47,466
- A complete stranger.
- Yes, I did...

387
00:38:47,514 --> 00:38:49,802
- I'm not psychotic.
- No, I know, I know...

388
00:38:50,015 --> 00:38:53,514
- Psychopathic perhaps, but not psychotic.
- I don't think you're a psychopath.

389
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:56,809
I kill people, doesn't that seem a bit
psychopatic to you?

390
00:38:56,896 --> 00:39:00,015
- Yeah, but...
- Don't get the wrong impression...

391
00:39:00,523 --> 00:39:03,311
Just because we share alot, doesn't mean
I'm not unsavory.

392
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:05,767
No, what you do is unsavory.

393
00:39:05,945 --> 00:39:08,233
You know what they say...
you are what you do.

394
00:39:24,918 --> 00:39:26,626
- Thanks.
- Thanks.

395
00:39:30,674 --> 00:39:32,381
Tell me...

396
00:39:34,093 --> 00:39:37,711
Will Bean stay with you
if this job doesn't come through?

397
00:39:37,846 --> 00:39:39,174
What?

398
00:39:39,222 --> 00:39:43,219
Will Bean stay with you if you continue
this losing-streak without any end?

399
00:39:43,892 --> 00:39:47,675
- If she ever left me, I'd fall apart...
- You're not answering my question.

400
00:39:50,690 --> 00:39:52,564
To be quite honest...

401
00:39:54,234 --> 00:39:57,021
... I don't know how much faith
the woman have left in her.

402
00:40:04,241 --> 00:40:05,653
Comforting me?

403
00:40:09,038 --> 00:40:11,114
Just change the subject, please.

404
00:40:11,206 --> 00:40:13,079
- I will.
- Something sunnier!

405
00:40:13,165 --> 00:40:16,416
Sunnier...! Absolutely.

406
00:40:17,169 --> 00:40:19,293
In fact there's something
I'd wanted to talk to you about.

407
00:40:19,338 --> 00:40:20,748
- A favor, really.
- Sure.

408
00:40:20,797 --> 00:40:24,000
- It's pretty big, it's a pretty big favor.
- It's okey.

409
00:40:24,050 --> 00:40:26,837
See... the thing is...

410
00:40:26,970 --> 00:40:28,796
...I could use your help.

411
00:40:29,471 --> 00:40:31,713
- Help with what?
- I'm down here...

412
00:40:32,598 --> 00:40:35,268
I finish my other job early,
so I let it be known.

413
00:40:35,309 --> 00:40:36,684
- "Let it be known"?
- Yes.

414
00:40:36,768 --> 00:40:39,307
To the powers that made
that I was available.

415
00:40:40,605 --> 00:40:42,894
- The powers of B?
- Yeah, anyway...

416
00:40:43,024 --> 00:40:46,439
They called me, emergency...
it has to happen today.

417
00:40:46,985 --> 00:40:48,728
Another job?

418
00:40:51,655 --> 00:40:55,273
The thing is...
I could really use your help.

419
00:41:00,747 --> 00:41:02,455
You're kidding right now?

420
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:05,246
I'm as serious as an erections-problem.

421
00:41:08,545 --> 00:41:11,082
- I can't help you, Julian.
- You could.

422
00:41:11,464 --> 00:41:14,001
I could, but I can't...
I'm not gonna help you-

423
00:41:14,091 --> 00:41:16,842
- to kill an innocent man.
- Who says he's innocent?

424
00:41:16,884 --> 00:41:18,509
- This is ridiculous!
- You'll just be assisting.

425
00:41:18,553 --> 00:41:20,212
- No!
-You just have to go out...

426
00:41:20,429 --> 00:41:24,675
I'm not listening.
I can't hear you, I can't hear you.

427
