You're being childish.

428
00:41:27,435 --> 00:41:29,262
You're being childish.

429
00:41:30,020 --> 00:41:33,021
You're being childish.
All I'm asking you to do, is just go...

430
00:41:33,357 --> 00:41:36,392
Alright, alright.
I won't tell you.

431
00:41:36,817 --> 00:41:38,442
- Good.
- Won't mention it.

432
00:41:38,485 --> 00:41:39,599
Great!

433
00:41:39,736 --> 00:41:42,061
All I'm saying, that all you have to do
is trip on the street right next to him.

434
00:41:42,113 --> 00:41:43,311
I can't believe you said that...

435
00:41:43,365 --> 00:41:46,779
Just trip and fall in about half an hour so
his body get turned, and look the other way.

436
00:41:46,825 --> 00:41:48,236
No way.

437
00:41:50,369 --> 00:41:52,410
50.000 dollars.
That's what I got paid.

438
00:41:52,456 --> 00:41:53,948
- No!
- It's alot of money.

439
00:41:53,997 --> 00:41:55,622
Cash.
And it could be real interesting.

440
00:41:55,666 --> 00:41:57,290
No! I said no!

441
00:41:57,334 --> 00:41:59,077
He's a prick, Danny!
A real prick!

442
00:41:59,127 --> 00:42:03,124
I don't give a darn who he is,
or what he did, or anything like that.

443
00:42:03,380 --> 00:42:06,548
I'm not gonna help you, Julian.
I'm not gonna do that!

444
00:42:07,467 --> 00:42:09,922
And if you bring it up again, I'll leave.

445
00:42:16,516 --> 00:42:17,845
- Fine.
- Fine.

446
00:42:17,893 --> 00:42:20,050
- Change the subject.
- Good, you do.

447
00:42:22,771 --> 00:42:24,514
- Change it...
- You.

448
00:42:24,564 --> 00:42:26,391
- Fine.
- Okey.

449
00:42:28,818 --> 00:42:31,523
When I was a kid,
I wanted to be a cheerleader.

450
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:36,489
Really?
A cheerleader?

451
00:42:36,532 --> 00:42:40,612
Yeah. I wanted to be thrown in the air
and march in the band.

452
00:42:42,913 --> 00:42:44,371
