459
00:43:08,350 --> 00:43:10,592
Well then... it's nice knowing you.

460
00:43:10,643 --> 00:43:13,312
No... Julian.
Come on.

461
00:43:13,563 --> 00:43:15,140
You're just leaving?
You're gonna leave?

462
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:17,722
- I got business to attend to.
