471
00:43:50,676 --> 00:43:55,337
Things may still break in our favor,
their first instinct was to go with us,

472
00:43:55,471 --> 00:43:59,515
but they're getting pretty intense pressure
to sign with a Mexican company.

473
00:43:59,851 --> 00:44:02,519
I'm trying to get Antonio so I can
set up one more meeting -

474
00:44:02,644 --> 00:44:06,059
- with you guys tomorrow.
I call you when I hear something.

475
00:44:06,314 --> 00:44:09,065
So, hang in there... it's not over yet.

476
00:44:35,087 --> 00:44:36,795
Danny!

477
00:44:37,798 --> 00:44:39,624
Danny, it's Julian!

478
00:44:40,926 --> 00:44:43,594
Come on, Danny,
I just want to say I'm sorry.

479
00:44:43,719 --> 00:44:46,803
I know it's late,
and I'm a bit fucked up, but...

480
00:44:46,847 --> 00:44:48,555
I'm sorry.

481
00:44:49,265 --> 00:44:51,554
I'm a mess,
I'm a fuckup!

482
00:44:58,314 --> 00:45:01,231
